  "response": "To stay healthy, it's important to:\n\n1. Diet\n- Eat a balanced diet with plenty of fruits and vegetables\n- Limit processed foods, sugar, and unhealthy fats\n- Stay hydrated by drinking enough water\n\n2. Exercise\n- Get at least 150 minutes of moderate exercise per week\n- Include both cardio and strength training\n- Stay physically active daily\n\n3. Sleep\n- Aim for 7-9 hours of quality sleep per night\n- Maintain a consistent sleep schedule\n- Create a relaxing bedtime routine\n\n4. Mental Health\n- Manage stress through meditation, yoga, or relaxation techniques\n- Maintain social connections\n- Seek professional help if needed\n\n5. Regular Check-ups\n- Get annual medical and dental check-ups\n- Stay current on vaccinations\n- Undergo recommended health screenings\n\n6. Lifestyle Habits\n- Don't smoke\n- Limit alcohol consumption\n- Practice good hygiene\n- Wash hands frequently\n\n7. Additional Tips\n- Practice good posture\n- Take breaks from sitting\n- Protect yourself from sun damage\n- Maintain a healthy weight\n\nCombining these strategies can help you maintain overall health and well-being.",
